{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/seniors/protection-virus","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":" Protection from the virus","meta_description":"How to prevent the spreading of COVID-19","content":{"processed":"<h2>Recommendation</h2>\n<p>The most important rule is often mentioned - <strong>wear a face mask, wash your hands and keep the distance from others. </strong>Together with a minimum of social contacts, this rule is simple and very effective prevention against the COVID-19 disease.</p>\n<p>Do not go to places with a higher concentration of people unless it is necessary. There are volunteer groups that can bring your groceries right to your home. If you are planning to visit family, choose a walk together instead of staying in a closed room.</p>\n<h2> </h2>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/seniors/protection-virus"},"changed":"2020-11-10T22:12:35+00:00","valid_from":null,"langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-07T16:55:45+00:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"security"},"situation_type":{"name":"Seniors","path":{"alias":"/situations/seniors"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"elderly"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"Purpose of the measures","path":{"alias":"/situations/infection-and-general-measures/purpose-measures","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Measures on free movement","path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people/measures-free-movement","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Support and delivery services to risk groups and those infected","path":{"alias":"/situations/volunteering/support-and-delivery-services-risk-groups-and-those-infected","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"What is the purpose of face masks?","path":{"alias":"/situations/face-masks/what-purpose-face-masks","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Hand washing","path":{"alias":"/situations/hygiene/hand-washing","langcode":"en"}}]},"questions_answers":[],"update":null,"valid_to":null,"last